frames.caption: A whimsical wedding scene features two anthropomorphic cats dressed in elegant wedding attire, standing under a floral arch. The setting is a beautifully decorated outdoor venue with guests applauding in the background. The atmosphere is celebratory and magical, enhanced by the warm lighting and floral decorations.
frames.description: The scene depicts a unique wedding ceremony where two anthropomorphic cats are the bride and groom. They are standing under a lavish arch made of white flowers, surrounded by an audience of well-dressed guests. The setting is outdoors, with a lush, green backdrop and a golden path lined with petals.

frames.caption: A couple dressed in elegant wedding attire stands under a floral arch, sharing a tender moment. Both have white cat heads, adding a whimsical touch to the romantic scene. The background is adorned with soft lighting and floral decorations, enhancing the enchanting atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a wedding ceremony with a fantasy twist, as the couple has cat heads. They are dressed in formal wedding attire, standing under a beautifully decorated arch with flowers and lights, suggesting a celebration of love.
